15
00:00:29.063 --> 00:00:30.831
- I don't know.
- Oh. Emily.

16
00:00:30.864 --> 00:00:32.200
We are doing this.

17
00:00:32.233 --> 00:00:33.701
When is the last time
you allowed yourself

18
00:00:33.734 --> 00:00:35.002
